    display="Tickets"
    bodytext="On the 8-10. August 2025, we invite you to join the first LOST FARM FESTIVAL adventure. As part of a gathering of only a few hundred lostfarmers, in the unique landscape of SjÃ¦llands Odde, Denmark you will get the opportunity to experience over 30 acts and projects on an ambitious and independent festival that embraces experimenting and places the landscape, community, and art to the front." 
